#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "See the following <a cbot|function>function</a>: the bot will be <a cbot|wait>waiting</a> a proper amount of time for a certain task to be completed:"
msgstr "Voir la <a cbot|function>fonction</a> suivante : le robot sera en train d'<a cbot|wait>attendre</a> un temps approprié pour une certaine tâche à accomplir :"

#. type: Source code
#: ../E/switch.txt:9
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"public void WaitForTaskCompleted(object building)\n"
"{\n"
"\tint cat = building.category;\n"
"\t<a cbot|if>if</a> (cat == Converter) wait(15);\n"
"\telse if (cat == BotFactory) wait(15);\n"
"\telse if (cat == PowerPlant) wait(12);\n"
"\telse message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"public void WaitForTaskCompleted(object building)\n"
"{\n"
"\tint cat = building.category;\n"
"\t<a cbot|if>if</a> (cat == Converter) wait(15);\n"
"\telse if (cat == BotFactory) wait(15);\n"
"\telse if (cat == PowerPlant) wait(12);\n"
"\telse message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"}"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "This function can be also written using the <code>switch() {}</code> instruction:"
msgstr "Cette fonction peut également être écrite en utilisant l'instruction <code>switch() {}</code> :"

#. type: Source code
#: ../E/switch.txt:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"public void WaitForTaskCompleted(object building)\n"
"{\n"
"\tswitch (building.category)\n"
"\t{\n"
"\t\tcase Converter: wait(15); break;\n"
"\t\tcase BotFactory: wait(15); break;\n"
"\t\tcase PowerPlant: wait(12); break;\n"
"\t\tdefault: message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"\t}\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"public void WaitForTaskCompleted(object building)\n"
"{\n"
"\tswitch (building.category)\n"
"\t{\n"
"\t\tcase Converter: wait(15); break;\n"
"\t\tcase BotFactory: wait(15); break;\n"
"\t\tcase PowerPlant: wait(12); break;\n"
"\t\tdefault: message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"\t}\n"
"}"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Which way to write this kind of choice structures, is a matter of taste."
msgstr "Cette façon d'écrire ce genre de structures de choix est une question de goût."

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can also make cases like this:"
msgstr "Vous pouvez aussi faire des \"cases\" regroupés comme celui-ci :"

#. type: Source code
#: ../E/switch.txt:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"switch (building.category)\n"
"{\n"
"\tcase Converter:\n"
"\tcase BotFactory:\n"
"\t\twait(15); break;\n"
"\tcase PowerPlant: wait(12); break;\n"
"\tdefault: message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"switch (building.category)\n"
"{\n"
"\tcase Converter:\n"
"\tcase BotFactory:\n"
"\t\twait(15); break;\n"
"\tcase PowerPlant: wait(12); break;\n"
"\tdefault: message(\"Undefined wait time\", DisplayError);\n"
"}"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a object|convert>Converter</a> and <a object|factory>bot factory</a> have the same waiting time, so in order to not write the same instructions twice, we made multiple cases run the same code. In fact, all code after the highest case used will be executed if we do not <code><a cbot|break>break</a></code> it."
msgstr "La <a object|convert>raffinerie</a> et l'<a object|factory>usine de robots</a> ont le même temps d'attente, donc afin de ne pas écrire les mêmes instructions deux fois, nous avons fait exécuter le même code dans plusieurs cas. En fait, tout le code après le \"case\" le plus haut sera exécuté si nous ne faisons pas de <code><a cbot|break>break</a></code>."

#. type: Source code
#: ../E/switch.txt:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<c/>switch ( value )\n"
"{\n"
"\tcase value1: instructions1\n"
"\tcase value2: instructions2\n"
"\t...\n"
"\tcase valueN: instructionsN\n"
"\tdefault: instructionsDefault\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"<c/>switch ( value )\n"
"{\n"
"\tcase value1: \t\tinstructions1;\n"
"\t\tbreak;\n"
"\tcase value2: \t\tinstructions2;\n"
"\t\tbreak;\n"
"\t...\n"
"\tcase valueN: \t\tinstructionsN;\n"
"\t\tbreak;\n"
"\tdefault: \n"
"\t\tinstructionsDefault;\n"
"} <n/> Ici, ça ne ferait qu'une instruction selon le cas, \n"
"Si on étudie plutôt cette forme : \n"
"<c/> <c/>switch ( value )\n"
"{\n"
"\tcase value1: instructions1\n"
"\tcase value2: instructions2\n"
"\t...\n"
"\tcase valueN: instructionsN\n"
"\t\tbreak;\n"
"\tdefault: instructionsDefault\n"
"}"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "With this conditional structure you can execute <code>instructions1</code> or <code>instructions2</code> ... or <code>instructionsN</code> or <code>instructionsDefault</code> depending on the <code>value</code>."
msgstr "Avec cette structure conditionnelle, vous pouvez exécuter <code>instructions1</code> ou <code>instructions2</code> ou <code>instructionsN</code> ou <code>instructionsDefault</code> selon le <code> valeur</code> puis toutes les autres (tant qu'il n'y a pas de break et que le bloc du switch n'est pas terminé)."

#. type: Plain text
#: ../E/switch.txt:59
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If the <code>value</code> is equal to <code>value1</code>, <code>instructions1</code> to <code>N</code> (including <code>instructionsDefault</code>) are executed.\n"
"If the <code>value</code> is equal to <code>value2</code>, <code>instructions2</code> to <code>N</code> (including <code>instructionsDefault</code>) are executed.\n"
"And so on.\n"
"If the <code>value</code> is equal to <code>valueN</code>, <code>instructionsN</code> and <code>instructionsDefault</code> are executed.\n"
"If the <code>value</code> is not equal to any value in the given cases, <code>instructionsDefault</code> are executed."
msgstr ""
"Si <code>value</code> est égal à <code>value1</code>, alors on exécute <code>instructions1</code> jusqu'à <code>N</code> .\n"
"Si <code>value</code> est égal à <code>value2</code>, alors on exécute <code>instructions2</code> jusqu'à <code>N</code> .\n"
"etc...\n"
"Si <code>value</code> est égal à <code>valueN</code>, alors on exécute <code>instructionsN</code>.\n"
"Si <code>value</code> ne fait pas partie des valeurs citées dans les \"cases\", alors on exécute <code>instructionsDefault</code>."

